{"tid":1757364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"口水襲警判10個月！13拳打手足只判5個半月！","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T15:17:14.000Z","uid":231896,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d04c18712063fb21eedf3eba0582a58811873fb","tid":1757364,"uid":231896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"//6.26 示威者包圍警察總部，一名父親是退休警察的 43 歲無業男子，向高級警司吐口水及以噴漆塗污警總正門玻璃門，他早前承認參與非法集結、刑事毀壞及襲警，今午（26日）於東區裁判法院判刑。裁判官香淑嫻指，被告吐口水「污穢、骯髒、卑鄙，有可能傳播細菌」，判刑須具阻嚇性及懲罰性，判他監禁 10 個月，和賠償警方 1670 元。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MKUiDw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MKUiDw.jpg&h=5d640902&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b72011967e33d73e10fe4cd848761ec0a3d563d4","tid":1757364,"uid":314136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"香淑嫻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a3ff8b9d89c99b33de0be4add08838781041ab","tid":1757364,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:11:17.000Z","msg":"白衫拎刀斬黑衫 的士撞黑衫<br />\n<br />\n有錢收"},{"pid":"68142b108ef54b4cd198166f69d9414100606dc0","tid":1757364,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"等睇政府蒙面法上訴成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97182e85bd7a3c501fa6f354c917f50890b757d6","tid":1757364,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"Magnitsky Act 要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蘇惠德第一個<br />\n呢個口水官 第二個"},{"pid":"70e55e5c279f455b220e850370232c8681207588","tid":1757364,"uid":154258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"有險可守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778d0be9d24113b102d666dde9186ef275635554","tid":1757364,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":